        (3171, 642, 'Creativity Rules: Off Topic is a fun board game that gets the brain juices flowin’ and stirs up some hilarious conversations during friends and family game night.'),
        (3172, 642, 'How To Play: Draw a card to set the topics, and roll the die to set the letter that your responses must begin with. Flip the sand timer and you''re off! Race against time to write down answers for each topic that begin with the letter rolled.'),
        (3173, 642, 'Defend Your Answers: Coming up with answers is only part of the game. Debating answers with your friends and family is where the real fun happens!'),
        (3174, 642, 'What''s In The Box?! Each game box comes with everything you need for endless rounds of fun: a 20-sided die, 16 game cards, 8 white boards, 10 dry erase markers, and a 2 minute sand timer.'),
        (3175, 642, 'Fast Paced Fun: The perfect party game for adults to play with 2-8 players. The game for those with short attentions spans, (read: everyone) the pace is quick, the rules are simple, and games can be as brief as 30 minutes, or as fun as 90 minutes!'),
        (3176, 643, '🙌 𝗚𝗥𝗘𝗔𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗙𝗔𝗠𝗜𝗟𝗬 𝗙𝗨𝗡 𝗔𝗡𝗗 𝗣𝗔𝗥𝗧𝗜𝗘𝗦 - Bungee Table is a fast-paced game that''s easy to set up and learn, making it suitable for both kids and adults. It''s a great choice for family game nights, parties, or friendly competitions.'),
        (3177, 643, '🌟 𝗛𝗜𝗚𝗛-𝗤𝗨𝗔𝗟𝗜𝗧𝗬 𝗪𝗢𝗢𝗗𝗘𝗡 𝗚𝗔𝗠𝗘 - Handcrafted from solid wood with a smooth finish, this durable game is built to withstand intense play. Includes 10 extra pucks and 2 additional elastic bands, so you''ll have replacements whenever needed.'),
        (3178, 643, '🎁 𝗧𝗛𝗢𝗨𝗚𝗛𝗧𝗙𝗨𝗟 𝗚𝗜𝗙𝗧 𝗙𝗢𝗥 𝗔𝗡𝗬 𝗢𝗖𝗖𝗔𝗦𝗜𝗢𝗡 - A fun and engaging gift for Christmas, birthdays, or other special occasions. It comes in stylish packaging, ready to delight kids, friends, or family with hours of joy. Bring people together with a gift that sparks laughter and bonding.'),
        (3179, 643, '🎯 𝗦𝗞𝗜𝗟𝗟-𝗕𝗨𝗜𝗟𝗗𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝗚𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗣𝗟𝗔𝗬 - Designed to improve reflexes, focus, and fine motor skills while delivering hours of dynamic and skill-building fun. An effective way for kids to develop hand-eye coordination, cognitive abilities, and physical skills. Encourages screen-free play, fostering interactive and social fun with family and friends.'),
        (3180, 643, '🏕️ 𝗟𝗜𝗚𝗛𝗧𝗪𝗘𝗜𝗚𝗛𝗧 & 𝗣𝗢𝗥𝗧𝗔𝗕𝗟𝗘 𝗙𝗨𝗡 - Take the excitement of Bungee Table anywhere! Its lightweight design makes it easy to bring along to game nights, family trips, or outdoor gatherings. Transform any setting into a spontaneous tournament, offering entertainment and bonding opportunities for all ages.'),
        (3181, 644, 'BIRD COLLECTING: You are bird enthusiasts - researchers, bird watchers, ornithologists, and collectors - seeking to discover and attract a beautiful and diverse network of birds to your wildlife preserve.'),
        (3182, 644, 'BUILD YOUR ENGINE: Gain food tokens via custom dice in a birdfeeder dice tower, lay eggs using egg miniatures in a variety of colors, draw from over 170 unique bird cards and play them. Each bird extends a chain of powerful combinations in one of your habitats. Earn points, play new birds, help others, and many other abilities!'),
        (3183, 644, 'AWARD WINNER: 2019 winner of the prestigious Kennerspiel des Jahres award, along with many others!'),
        (3184, 644, 'COMPETITIVE: Medium-weight, card-driven board game from designer Elizabeth Hargrave. Includes swift-start pack for first time player guidance.'),
        (3185, 644, 'GORGEOUS ART: Beautifully illustrated by Natalia Rojas, Ana Maria Martinez Jaramillo, and Beth Sobel with a lovely realistic and naturalistic art style.'),
        (3186, 644, 'THOUGHTFULLY DESIGNED BIRD CARDS: Every element of the bird used on each card is tied to the theme and mechanisms of the cards: the type of nest and number of eggs that nest holds, the size of the birds and many of their abilities, the type of food that is needed to attract said bird, and where that bird will come to rest on your playmat.'),
        (3187, 644, 'THEMATICALLY DESIGNED MECHANISMS: Most bird cards have an ability that benefits you during the game. Many of these abilities tie into the nature of the bird represented on the card. For example, the parasitic nature of the cowbirds is used in the game by not allowing eggs to be placed on it but rather giving you the ability to place eggs in other birds’ nests, just like these birds use the nests of other birds in real life. The northern mockingbird imitates another bird in your habitat. Some bird powers allow you to tuck cards underneath them, like a raptor eating another smaller bird.'),
        (3188, 644, 'SOLO PLAY: Features an Automa to play against in a single player game for a fun solitaire experience. The Automa simulates an opponent for you to compete against, while your game as a player remains the same. On the Automa’s turn, flip a card to see what action it takes.'),
        (3189, 644, 'EXCELLENT GIFT: Great gift for families, teenagers, students, couples, and anyone who loves birds and nature.'),
        (3190, 644, 'CREATED BY WOMEN: Designed by Elizabeth Hargrave. Illustrated by Natalia Rojas, Ana Maria Martinez Jaramillo, and Beth Sobel.'),
        (3197, 647, '【Happy Family Time & Promote Friendship】:This stack attack toy is very suitable for children, teenagers, and adults.It is a popular interactive game in the game room.Suitable for 2 or more players. Whether indoors or outdoors, It can promote relationships very well. It''s also a good dialogue board game.'),
        (3198, 647, '【Fun and Easy】: This stack attack toy is not difficult to play, so our children can easily to learn. Children, parents, and friends will all love this stacking toy.This fun table top game is suitable for people over 3 years old.'),
        (3199, 647, '【Kind Service】:We have prepared a storage box for you so that you can find it at any time anywhere.The package includes: 48x stacked blocks, 1x base, and 22x card drawer.No matter at home, office, or coffee shop, all you need is a table then you can start playing games.'),
        (3200, 647, '【Perfect Game】: Suitable for parties, game nights, drinking games, and travel games. Great gift for Christmas, birthday, and Children''s Day.'),
        (3201, 647, '【ABS PLASTIC】: Made of ABS plastic materials. Plastic materials are lighter and easier for children to play.'),
        (3202, 648, 'Easy Assembly & Convenient Portability: Our jumbo 4-to-score game is effortlessly set up or disassembled for on-the-go fun at your next gathering. Tool-free assembly takes just minutes. Crafted from high-quality plastic, the entire game set weighs only 10 lbs, making it lightweight and easy to carry for outdoor use.'),
        (3203, 648, 'Premium Materials & Ultimate Durability: Carefully selected premium PE and PP materials ensure safety and durability. The smooth edges eliminate any risk of scratches during gameplay, providing a long-lasting and safe experience.'),
        (3204, 648, 'Height Adjustable for All Ages: Enjoy the flexibility of a height-adjustable game set suitable for both adults and children.'),
        (3205, 648, 'Fun for Everyone, Everywhere: Elevate your home entertainment with this connect game set suitable for various occasions, including backyard parties, birthdays, holidays, weddings, and friend gatherings. Ideal for users of all ages, both indoors and outdoors, it promises exciting and enjoyable family game nights.'),
        (3206, 648, 'Perfect Gift with Educational Benefits: Our colorful giant game toy makes an excellent gift for children, bringing surprise and hours of entertainment for birthdays or holidays. With its simple rules, this game not only entertains but also enhances children''s motor skills, hand-eye coordination, and cognitive abilities.'),
        (3207, 649, 'THE TABOO GAME FOR ADULTS ONLY: Pop Culture. NSFW. Snort laughs. Small Package. Party Game. The answer is … the Taboo Uncensored game. It''s the game of unspeakable … well, it''s so unspeakable we can''t even say it'),
        (3208, 649, 'SERIOUSLY, THIS TABOO GAME IS NOT THE ONE FOR KIDS: This Taboo Uncensored game for ages 17+ puts the "forbidden" in forbidden words for a hilarious adults-only game that will reveal a lot about your friends. Maybe too much'),
        (3209, 649, 'CLASSIC TABOO GAMEPLAY, UNAPOLOGETICALLY FILTHY CONTENT: Get your team to guess the word. Say whatever the (BLEEP) you want. Just don''t say any of the Taboo words or else the other team will call you out'),
        (3210, 649, 'ENHANCE GAME WITH FREE ONLINE TOOLS: Scan the in-pack QR code to play with the virtual buzzer, timer, and scoreboard – or stick with the included squeaker and sand timer. Either way, it''s a great travel game'),
        (3211, 649, 'PERFECT GIFT FOR ADULTS WHO LIKE IT HOT: And for those who don''t, look for the original Taboo board game'),
