        (3214, 650, 'Power up spaces: The game instructions include options for playing the classic trouble game or using power up spaces'),
        (3215, 650, 'Pop-o-matic bubble: The iconic pop-o-matic die roller bubble is fun to press, and it keeps the die from getting lost'),
