        (3246, 655, 'Fun Dartboard Game for Any Age - Containing 13 inch magnetic dartboard, set of 12 safe magnetic darts, comes with darts and instructions on how high to place it on the wall. It is the perfect size, the darts are very magnetic and can stick to the board extremely well. Only installing on walls,easy to use for kids or adults.'),
